message.en_US: Hello there, did you want to form a party?
I see your party is already full.\. At least according to the usual rules.
No matter, I'd be happy to join you guys anyway.
Ok, let's go!\. You can always come back here and I'd be happy to join even if your party is full.
You can also \c[3]contact\c[0] me through Direct Link if you want me to join a full party.
I'll be here if you change your mind.
Hello, Lea!\. Reckon your party needs a \c[3]fourth\c[0] member?
We meet again, Lea!\. Want me to join you?
Ok, I would be glad to join you guys!
I'll be here if you need me.\. As always...\!
You can also just call me on \c[3]Direct Link\c[0] in the future.
